name: Exploring sites
description: The body as the essence of adaptation to other realities, as a bridge to explore and seek new ways of understanding and coping, as a way to sensitively and directly feel what surrounds us and continue paths. The body as a receiver, as a curious dimension that wishes to transgress barriers and limits. The body as what is affected, what suffers, but wakes up and looks forward. The body as what we are and without fear of being sincere.
